OL,3,C'Resurfacing blitz' to tackle potholes
OL,4,Cwith roads to be closed for a week
OL,6,FIn Kent, the number of reported
OL,7,Fpotholes were at a nine-year high at
OL,8,Fthe start of the year.
OL,10,FThe slurry being used in Brighton and
OL,11,FHove forms a watertight layer designed
OL,12,Fto prevent wear and tear and reduce
OL,13,Ffuture maintenance.
OL,15,FAfter being applied, the road can be
OL,16,Fready for use in around 20 minutes
OL,17,Fthough the city council says it can
OL,18,Fonly be applied 47 hours after being
OL,19,Ffilled.
